JACKSONVILLE Florida  Tiger Woods and his Swedish girlfriendElin Nordegren are engaged PERIOD

The golfers agent Mark Steinberg of IMG confirmed thecouples engagement to The Associated Press on Friday but declinedto give details PERIOD

 Nordegrensfather Thomas told the Swedish newspaper Expressen PERIOD 

Thomas Nordegren a correspondent for Swedish Radio inWashington could not immediately be reached for comment by theAP PERIOD

Ashley Cocks a spokesman for the Shamwari Game Reserve in SouthAfrica said in a statement that Woods proposed to Nordegren whileat the game park outside Port Elizabeth PERIOD Woods had been inFancourt South Africa for the Presidents Cup which endedSunday PERIOD

The proposal came during a walk at sunset Tuesday he saidadding that when the couple left Friday aboard a private jetNordegren had a 

Nordegrens mother Barbro Holmberg who is Swedens migrationminister had no comment PERIOD

Woods  and Nordegren a 23yearold model have been datingfor nearly two years PERIOD

The South African Broadcasting Corp PERIOD also reported theengagement saying the couple spent the night under the stars insleeping bags and prepared their own food PERIOD

Woods and his entourage later left Port Elizabeth via Barbadosto the United States SABC reported PERIOD

Expressen said the date and location of the wedding were notdisclosed but that it was likely to take place in Sweden PERIOD

Woods caddie Steve Williams of New Zealand got engaged theweekend before the Presidents Cup PERIOD
